      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THUMANI (2) has a strong overall record having six wins and 13 places from 21 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (19.96) over 342m at Angle Park. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. Looks well placed here and should prove hard to beat again. BINNAWAY WIZARD (1) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 6 lengths (19.98) at Angle Park in a Grade 6 over 342m. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Overdue and expected to feature again. KILCOY GEM (8) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (19.93) at this track. Got the money at her only try from this box. Expected to feature. ONE MARGARITA (5) is worth including after a top-three finish in slick time most recently.",
